<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7677020>
    dc:description "Figs. 1-3. Behavior of Melophorus anderseni. 1. The impassable living nest plug of Iridomyrmex sanguineus, formed of heads ant heads. 2. M. anderseni entering and leaving the sanguineus nest unmolested. 3. Rubbing of M. anderseni on I. sanguineus. This procedure lasts less than a minute, without any defense of sanguineus worker." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7677020/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

